00:14:42,760 --> 00:14:45,120
We laid out every single UI element

262
00:14:45,120 --> 00:14:47,681
that had to be displayed onto the screen

263
00:14:47,681 --> 00:14:52,102
and identified what is the most important information that

264
00:14:52,102 --> 00:14:54,582
will impact the player from moment to moment

