00:15:55,514 --> 00:15:57,996
and you'll see an example of that moving forward.

283
00:15:57,996 --> 00:16:01,739
We've reclaimed real estate

284
00:16:01,739 --> 00:16:06,363
by moving the tool information into one succinct location

285
00:16:06,363 --> 00:16:08,205
and introducing a radial menu,

286
00:16:08,205 --> 00:16:10,887
condensing the swapping between tools

287
00:16:10,887 --> 00:16:13,610
into one spot that's hidden off the screen.

288
00:16:15,339 --> 00:16:19,260
Several usability concerns have already kind of been addressed through this,

