00:16:59,819 --> 00:17:03,923
and we've reduced or removed any post effects

301
00:17:03,923 --> 00:17:05,544
from the talking head to ensure

302
00:17:05,544 --> 00:17:07,266
that that is particularly legible

303
00:17:07,266 --> 00:17:08,847
at any given point in the game.

304
00:17:09,947 --> 00:17:13,450
Now, I do want to say an accessibility pass

