323
00:18:22,211 --> 00:18:30,497
This is a particularly big feat and could honestly warrant an entire talk of its own,

324
00:18:30,497 --> 00:18:33,300
but I'm not going to focus on that.

325
00:18:34,770 --> 00:18:41,340
Luckily, we are in early access, so we have access to players through our Discord, Twitch,

326
00:18:41,340 --> 00:18:47,370
Twitter, to give us feedback, and we get to see the impact of some of these decisions as we're making them.

327
00:18:51,031 --> 00:18:56,014
So the goal for this interface was to make it as realistic as possible

328
00:18:56,014 --> 00:18:58,056
