00:19:35,759 --> 00:19:39,382
Narratively, Lynx doesn't give you the nice fancy tech.

340
00:19:39,382 --> 00:19:42,025
That's reserved for the upper class.

341
00:19:42,025 --> 00:19:45,468
But rather what you get is the retrofitted hand-me-down tech

342
00:19:45,468 --> 00:19:47,189
called Trevorware Tech in the game,

