00:19:51,663 --> 00:19:55,364
So here's an example of your HUD kind of reacting

345
00:19:55,364 --> 00:20:00,444
to the external forces when you are cutting the ship,

346
00:20:00,444 --> 00:20:05,926
really embracing the fact that this screen is on your helmet.

347
00:20:05,926 --> 00:20:10,286
It is not modern technology, and if you take damage,

348
00:20:10,286 --> 00:20:11,767
so does your helmet, so does your suit.

349
00:20:11,767 --> 00:20:16,147
We've also added stylized elements like brackets

350
00:20:16,147 --> 00:20:19,788
and acronyms to bring the player closer

351
00:20:19,788 --> 00:20:21,448
to the fighter pilot feel.

