00:20:32,443 --> 00:20:36,884
But this, and there's UI elements that probably wouldn't exist,

356
00:20:36,884 --> 00:20:39,604
and for sure would not exist on a fighter pilot HUD.

357
00:20:39,604 --> 00:20:42,485
But this was a conscious decision that we made.

358
00:20:42,485 --> 00:20:46,986
To ensure that we made room for every element in the game.

359
00:20:48,033 --> 00:20:52,776
And we tried to bring the player back into that sense of presence

360
00:20:52,776 --> 00:20:58,620
using the post effects and audio, as you saw in the slide before,

361
00:20:58,620 --> 00:21:01,842
to set that or to sell that realism.

