00:21:31,833 --> 00:21:33,714
What a segue, almost like I planned it.

372
00:21:33,714 --> 00:21:37,036
So narratively, when you die, there

373
00:21:37,036 --> 00:21:38,957
and honestly, there's many ways to die in this game.

