00:22:29,189 --> 00:22:31,272
of, oh, I'm pretty expendable to this company.

386
00:22:32,640 --> 00:22:34,740
So this is the new death experience.

387
00:22:34,740 --> 00:22:39,861
You've died of asphyxiation, and what you see now

388
00:22:39,861 --> 00:22:41,441
is being completely cloned.

